                        <interp inst="t18370918-name-1262" type="given" value="WILLIAM LEWIS"></interp>WILLIAM LEWIS KETCHER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an officer. I took him into custody.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I left home about three o'clock to go to my uncle's—I saw two boys going along—they ran away and dropped the handkerchief—I took it up and put it into my pocket—the gentleman immediately came up and gave me in charge.</p>
